{"tid":2185400,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解昆蟲唔會演化出識避開食肉植物","createTime":"2020-09-02T08:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T04:34:41.000Z","uid":148749,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"567428954c695724684baeb7e664c3e701a520ca","tid":2185400,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"所以生物都有種本能去避開危險<br />\n遇到大型既生物會識走 就算有D體積細過自己都知惹唔過<br />\n一出世就知邊D打得過 邊D打唔過<br />\n但係點解明明食肉植物係對自己有危險 但過左咁多個世代<br />\n昆蟲都唔識分出食肉植物"},{"pid":"6fea8676ec143983fbd2df6868efbf2fcef02c3d","tid":2185400,"uid":37869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"道高一尺 魔高一丈"},{"pid":"587419eb8fe631b04799026af8340970201b5c94","tid":2185400,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"演化係淘汰制 食肉植物淘汰唔到避唔開佢嘅昆蟲"},{"pid":"d1e7c8fa2f4db15ecfc34be2d9c0918280dadb79","tid":2185400,"uid":306337,"like":25,"dislike":10,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"因為掂到嘅都死咗, 冇倖存. 冇呢個經驗落去, 下一代根本唔知呢樣嘢有危險"},{"pid":"78fa32b8270668fbba0b016f993e6c9d3f77027f","tid":2185400,"uid":86426,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"因為適者生存個理論要某個基因(例如:Size)會易D死先運用到<br />\n如果食蟲植物唔會簡基因,咩蟲都食,記憶又唔會遺傳落去<br />\n所以昆蟲唔會進化到分得食肉植物<br />\n利申: DSE 冇讀BIO"},{"pid":"5a2c223ce5c2146fbb38aac5d56596565f87251a","tid":2185400,"uid":65473,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:49:30.000Z","msg":"有個靚女喺你面前畀你屌<br />\n屌完短十年命<br />\n你狗唔狗衝？"},{"pid":"75cf195680ef8483bd448e73091f639758413bc6","tid":2185400,"uid":274435,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"因為食肉植物又會進化去吸引啲識避既昆蟲"},{"pid":"c8a5b088cc88279abe94b35aa6e103801860a736","tid":2185400,"uid":346260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as