a3324cbf9f01dce3d9c83994c51d874bad5d08","tid":2185400,"uid":113185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"適者生存應該係睇仲在生嗰啲生物多啲<br />\n例如基因突變令到某啲昆蟲見到食肉植物會覺得好驚/嘔心<br />\n會專登避開嘅話 咁帶住呢種基因嘅昆蟲存活率就會高啲 最尾可能演化到所有昆蟲都識避開食肉植物<br />\n但係依家演化唔到 可能係因為呢啲昆蟲被食而喪生嘅比率實在太低<br />\n低到唔足以篩走「冇避開食肉植物本能」嘅昆蟲<br />\n利申: 9up"},{"pid":"6946afc167803a53bc4cff0151a6d4f2c2193779","tid":2185400,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b355a4817fcc637a64ffd2cd967a342880c1059","tid":2185400,"uid":130797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:53:44.000Z","msg":"點解豬牛羊呢d唔識進化成皮包骨<br />\n啖啖肉好難叫人唔食左你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我地人類又同佢地配種配到啖啖肉"},{"pid":"7f2408f8d95f5e9ed63812c7c3363882e9e3314a","tid":2185400,"uid":47901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb6820a3d7d4eb9bdeae5f575c1224a1b492f863","tid":2185400,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:54:03.000Z","msg":"好似非洲d動物咁多年都係係河邊或渡河時俾鱷魚食左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"甚致人類咁多年都仲會熱死或高處跌死，淨呢兩樣都就已在進化上搏鬥左n年，再係進入文明之後再搏鬥多幾千年（發明左好多野去防止），到今日都有人熱死或跌死（例如地盤工人，軍人，行山人）"},{"pid":"bb41c7d21163415086236096115d628c571822d0","tid":2185400,"uid":286155,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e8ee3ed9be68fce44d5d9267685e1526ddad2b41","tid":2185400,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8855c9595c54e30681c9f14cb09071f618a99264","tid":2185400,"uid":283189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75cf195680ef8483bd448e73091f639758413bc6","tid":2185400,"uid":274435,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"因為食肉植物又會進化去吸引啲識避既昆蟲"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"昆蟲又會進化去避開識捉佢哋嘅食肉植物"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"食肉植物：你估得你地班昆蟲識得進化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dv0My99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdv0My99.png&h=bcfaedcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35a098592f0cd5c0fd22d33214ca7d6eaa275b88","tid":2185400,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"生物都有種本能去避開危險<br />\n但生物無本能識得分邊d野危險邊d野唔危險<br />\n<br />\n危唔危險係靠前人教 / 食過屎先知<br />\n<br />\n即係熱滾水好危險，但bb仔唔知，要父母教或者掂過一次食過屎先知危險。<br />\n<br />\n但昆蟲就無父母會教，到佢食屎果次已經死了。"},{"pid":"5057fd724e97abeaccb56bbe222fd2e8ab11c9d6","tid":2185400,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7f2408f8d95f5e9ed63812c7c3363882e9e3314a","tid":2185400,"uid":47901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb6820a3d7d4eb9bdeae5f575c1224a1b492f863","tid":2185400,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:54:03.000Z","msg":"好似非洲d動物咁多年都係係河邊或渡河時俾鱷魚食左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:01:24.000Z","msg":"甚致人類咁多年都仲會熱死或高處跌死，淨呢兩樣都就已在進化上搏鬥左n年，再係進入文明之後再搏鬥多幾千年（發明左好多野去防止），到今日都有人熱死或跌死（例如地盤工人，軍人，行山人）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"點解唔演化寒底同行路帶眼？"},{"pid":"dc63b3c1d5efd11626bf32f3eda558aa7e2f075b","tid":2185400,"uid":77968,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"因為食肉植物都識進化，而且證明左食肉植物呢啲陷阱好有效，中過呢啲陷阱嘅昆蟲都死得8899，無法將記憶/求生方法刻落DNA ，令下一代得到避開嘅方法<br />\n<br />\n更細思極恐嘅係，古代人類社會之中有唔少奇怪生物傳說，但後來佢哋消失曬，到底係科學昌明左，啲迷信消失左，抑或係怪物進化左，所有見過佢哋嘅人都失蹤/死亡，個傳說無法流傳落去警告後代?"},{"pid":"c2340314f4dca774681a1c3a237c42171c31ce03","tid":2185400,"uid":199227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"昆蟲繁殖速度&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;食肉植物食蟲嘅速度<br />\n食肉植物對昆蟲族群黎講微不足道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"c8a5b088cc88279abe94b35aa6e103801860a736","tid":2185400,"uid":346260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T08:52:53.000Z","msg":"唔該借個位嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有用 post ,樓主可唔可以置頂？唔該曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係想保護自己同身邊嘅人？即刻入嚟睇吓!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2185179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2185179</a>"}}